CHOLERA - RUSSIA (MOSCOW)
*************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Cholera - Italy, Russia 980710222945
Cholera - Russia (Moscow) 970717222457
Cholera - Russia (Moscow)(02): type O139 970718170033

Date: Fri, 31 Jul 1998 16:07:42 GMT-3
Source: News media, 30 Jul 98
Via: John Woodall <WOODALL@SERVER.BIOQMED.UFRJ.BR>

A third cholera case has been diagnosed in Moscow. The patient is a sixty
seven year-old woman who was hospitalized for symptoms of food poisoning.
She is reported to be recovering.
Health officials are downplaying the potential for a more widespread
cholera outbreak.
